### 门店列表（分页 + 筛选）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stores?page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 门店列表（按名称筛选）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stores?page=1&page_size=10&name=旗舰店
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取门店详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建门店
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "朝阳旗舰店",
  "code": "store_001",
  "address": "北京市朝阳区建国路88号"
}

### 更新门店
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "朝阳旗舰店(装修升级)",
  "address": "北京市朝阳区建国路99号"
}

### 删除门店
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stores/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
